steps.section: Requested processing protocol for Donation following Brain Death Declaration (DBD)
steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"596d3","text":"Organ Procurement Organization Recovery Team prepares for organ recovery as consistent with organ transplant protocol with cross clamp and in situ cold flush body cooling with minimal warm ischemic time.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"20i4k","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"asefh","text":"Includes flush with Perfadex or similar organ transplant buffer, until solution runs clear","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

steps.section: Requested processing protocol for Donation following Brain Death Declaration (DBD)
steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"d7c59","text":"Complete a minimum back-table lung flush with transplant buffer of 500ml into the pulmonary artery and 500ml into the pulmonary vein. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"46tb","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ev5j3","text":"Do not flush with saline.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"87g34","text":"Do not wrap in surgical towel.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

steps.section: Requested processing protocol for Donation following Brain Death Declaration (DBD)
steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"eenku","text":"Staple, clamp, or tie the trachea closed prior to shipping. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

steps.section: Requested processing protocol for Donation following Brain Death Declaration (DBD)
steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"dsukf","text":"Place Lung(s) in a Specimen Bag and submerge with chilled Perfadex or similar. Triple bag the tissue.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

steps.section: Requested processing protocol for Donation following Cardiac Death /Arrest(DCD)
steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"ebfgt","text":"Organ Procurement Organization / Recovery Team prepares for organ recovery as quickly following Cardiac Arrest while in comfort care as authorized by next of kin.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

steps.section: Requested processing protocol for Donation following Cardiac Death /Arrest(DCD)
steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"478jt","text":"Remainder of organ / tissue recovery should be as consistent with organ transplant protocol (section above) as possible.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c1ar0","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5q55v","text":"Includes organ flush with Perfadex or similar organ transplant buffer until solution runs clear.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
